# Control Flow in Procedures

## IF Statement:
```sql
IF salary > 50000 THEN
    SELECT 'High Salary';
ELSE
    SELECT 'Low Salary';
END IF;
```

---

# CASE Statement:
```sql
CASE
    WHEN salary > 50000 THEN 'High'
    ELSE 'Low'
END
```

---

